": \"\"\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            \"item_name\": \"避震器套装\",\r\n            \"id\": 2,\r\n            \"model_number\": \"3AAA.TJ.A1.000\"\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            \"item_name\": \"\",\r\n            \"id\": 3,\r\n            \"model_number\": \"3AAA.TJ.A1.000\"\r\n        }\r\n    ],\r\n    \"page\": {\r\n        \"totalResult\": 3,\r\n        \"showCount\": 1000,\r\n        \"totalPage\": 1,\r\n        \"currentPage\": 1\r\n    },\r\n    \"status\": 200\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 返回说明\r\n|参数名称|参数类型|参数描述|\r\n|--|--|--|\r\n|msg|String|返回说明|\r\n|total|int|数据总条数|\r\n|data|Array|数据体|\r\n|page|JsonObject|关于分页的数据|\r\n\r\n', '1', '0', '2017-12-13 12:21:22', '2017-12-13 11:07:51');
